<section id="fs-idm361138864">
<title>Operations and Management Plan</title>
<para id="fs-idm342643808">In this section, outline how you will manage your company. Describe its organizational structure. Here you can address the form of ownership and, if warranted, include an organizational chart/structure. Highlight the backgrounds, experiences, qualifications, areas of expertise, and roles of members of the management team. This is also the place to mention any other stakeholders, such as a board of directors or advisory board(s), and their relevant relationship to the founder, experience and value to help make the venture successful, and professional service firms providing management support, such as accounting services and legal counsel.</para>
<para id="fs-idm344234176"><link target-id="fs-idm326177680"/> shows a sample operations and management plan for La Vida Lola.</para>
