</list>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm358484192">
<problem id="fs-idm326722192">
<para id="fs-idm360229664">Which of these is not the purpose of a business plan?</para>
<list id="fs-idm360689712" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>thoroughly explain a business idea and how it will be carried out</item>
<item>planning tool and working plan over the course of several years</item>
<item>requirement to start a business</item>
<item>planning for “what-if” scenarios and explore new options</item>
</list>
</problem>
</exercise>
